As an AI language model, I do not have access to the real-time data. However, according to the University of Pennsylvania School of Medicine, some of their current top-ranked research areas include:

1. Genetics and Epigenetics
2. Cancer Biology and Treatment
3. Neurodegenerative Disorders
4. Infectious Diseases
5. Precision Medicine and Genomics
6. Immunology and Autoimmunity
7. Metabolism and Diabetes
8. Cardiac and Vascular Biology
9. Regenerative Medicine
10. Health Policy and Health Outcomes Research.
